description: Sublattices of index n in generic 6-dimensional lattice.
references: M. Baake, "Solution of coincidence problem...", in R. V. Moody, ed., Math. of Long-Range Aperiodic Order, Kluwer 1997, pp. 9-44.
links: Index entries for sequences related to sublattices
formula: f(Q, n)=Sum d*f(Q-1, d), d|n; here Q=6.Multiplicative with a(p^e) = product (p^(e+k)-1)/(p^k-1), k=1..5.Dirichlet g.f. zeta(s)*zeta(s-1)*zeta(s-2)*zeta(s-3)*zeta(s-4)*zeta(s-5). Dirichlet convolution of A038992 with A000584. - R. J. Mathar, Mar 31 2011
author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
extensions: Offset changed from 0 to 1 . - R. J. Mathar, Mar 31 2011
